you might have.

542
00:51:32,657 --> 00:51:34,742
- When?
- Tonight.

543
00:51:34,826 --> 00:51:37,704
Meet him at the 7th Street
stockyards.

544
00:51:37,787 --> 00:51:40,665
All right,
but promise you'll be careful.

545
00:51:40,748 --> 00:51:44,377
Of course I will,
funny-face, for you.

546
00:51:45,628 --> 00:51:48,423
I've got to go. See you tomorrow.

547
00:51:48,506 --> 00:51:52,343
Are you sure you won't have
something to eat?

548
00:52:17,493 --> 00:52:19,746
Ludwig?

549
00:52:19,829 --> 00:52:22,916
- Drebin?
- Yeah, l'm Drebin.

550
00:52:22,999 --> 00:52:26,753
