to do her tonight, here.

559
00:53:52,714 --> 00:53:57,677
- We better be on the lookout.
- Excuse me, ma'am, security.

560
00:53:59,512 --> 00:54:04,225
- What's the meaning of this?
- Relax! Nothing will happen.

561
00:54:04,308 --> 00:54:07,395
- I didn't do anything.
- Yeah? What about this?

562
00:54:07,478 --> 00:54:11,816
You think we were born yesterday?
You didn't do anything, huh?

563
00:54:11,899 --> 00:54:13,484
I got rights!

564
00:54:13,568 --> 00:54:16,821
Ed, he's got a picture of your wife!

565
00:54:16,904 --> 00:54:18,948
Ethel!

566
00:54:20,533 --> 00:54:23,202
All right,
