567
00:54:23,286 --> 00:54:26,664
That's all right, Frank.
Let's get in the hall.

568
00:54:37,467 --> 00:54:39,510
Are you enjoying yourself, my dear?

569
00:54:39,594 --> 00:54:44,223
I'm so excited to be here.
I appreciate your inviting me.

570
00:54:44,307 --> 00:54:48,144
Pleasure's all mine.
Perhaps afterwards we can...

571
00:54:50,354 --> 00:54:52,190
- Drebin!
- Frank!

572
00:54:52,273 --> 00:54:55,401
You're both right.
Surprised to see me, Mr Ludwig?

573
00:54:55,484 --> 00:54:58,404
This is not the time
