a peek-a-boo session with bullets,

582
00:55:29,060 --> 00:55:32,313
set up by someone
who's been playing me like a violin.

583
00:55:32,396 --> 00:55:35,191
Funny-face,
what are you talking about?

584
00:55:35,274 --> 00:55:39,320
