615
00:58:02,171 --> 00:58:05,466
He went to the chair
two years ago, Frank.

616
00:58:05,549 --> 00:58:08,928
Well...what's the use?

617
00:58:09,011 --> 00:58:12,097
What good are these damn awards
and citations?

618
00:58:12,181 --> 00:58:13,807
Frank...

