631
00:58:55,140 --> 00:58:57,518
- Where?
- At the baseball game.

632
00:58:57,601 --> 00:59:01,021
The Queen will be there
as Ludwig's guest.

633
00:59:01,105 --> 00:59:05,234
Is Ludwig going to shoot her
