636
00:59:11,115 --> 00:59:14,118
- I'll go with you.
- Stay with Ludwig

637
00:59:14,201 --> 00:59:17,454
- to allay suspicion.
- OK, let's go!

638
00:59:17,538 --> 00:59:19,331
Wait! Wait!

