00:59:52,448 --> 00:59:56,952
Good afternoon.
We're coming live from the Big A,

646
00:59:57,035 --> 01:00:00,205
where the California Angels
meet the Seattle Mariners

647
01:00:00,289 --> 01:00:04,626
in their showdown
for the Division League.

648
01:00:04,710 --> 01:00:08,464
Hello! l'm Curt Gowdy,
along with Jim Palmer,

649
01:00:08,547 --> 01:00:11,633
