650
01:00:11,717 --> 01:00:14,928
Dick Enberg and Dr Joyce Brothers.

651
01:00:15,012 --> 01:00:17,765
Join us for this
all-important ball game.

652
01:00:17,848 --> 01:00:19,600
And a special game it is.

653
01:00:19,683 --> 01:00:23,520
