internationally-renowned opera star,

682
01:02:33,525 --> 01:02:35,944
Enrico Pallazzo!

683
01:02:38,864 --> 01:02:42,367
Ladies and gentlemen,
let us honour America,

684
01:02:42,451 --> 01:02:48,415
as Mr Pallazzo will now sing
our national anthem.

685
01:04:10,038 --> 01:04:14,125
