690
01:04:41,069 --> 01:04:44,948
showing some unusual moments
in baseball over the years!

691
01:05:05,218 --> 01:05:07,262
Sorry, fellas!

692
01:05:35,123 --> 01:05:37,417
How about that?

693
01:05:39,169 --> 01:05:40,962
Ladies and gentlemen,

694
01:05:41,046 --> 01:05:45,592
now taking the field -
your California Angels!

695
01:05:52,432 --> 01:05:55,518
