here to enjoy the game.

704
01:06:38,394 --> 01:06:41,564
What d'you say, Cummings?
Are we gonna do this today?

705
01:06:41,648 --> 01:06:43,274
Do what?

706
01:06:43,358 --> 01:06:45,151
Play ball!

707
01:06:48,279 --> 01:06:51,241
Frank! Al, it's Frank!

708
01:06:56,204 --> 01:07:00,667
The game's under way. Dave Spiwack
ready to face Jay Johnstone!

709
01:07:20,061 --> 01:07:23,231
- Nothing to report.
